<hw>brouhaha</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the confused noise of
many voices.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hubbub, uproar.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a confused disturbance far greater than its cause
